<lb ed="I" n="0257a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 97</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0257a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>瓽仲義八十人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0257a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0257a0101">□大覺<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">寺</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">軒</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">義</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">世</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">真</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">容</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">寂</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">默</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">彰</unclear>□□
<lb ed="I" n="0257a02" type="honorific"/>之年。爰及□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">室</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">肇</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">現</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">閻</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">浮</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">生</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">滅</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">相</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">因</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">報</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">應</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">斯</unclear>□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0257a03" type="honorific"/>以慧心獨悟<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">智</unclear>。自登彼<note n="0257001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB01437"/>＝岸【史】</note><app n="0257001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB01437"/></rdg></app>之果。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聾</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">所</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">見</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0257a04" type="honorific"/><note n="0257002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣱵＝永【史】</note><app n="0257002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">永</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣱵</rdg></app>沉<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">苦</unclear>海之際。佛弟子邑主都督瓽仲義。邑師比
<lb ed="I" n="0257a05" type="honorific"/>丘智盛。合邑子八十人<note n="0257003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䒭＝等【史】</note><app n="0257003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">等</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䒭</rdg></app>。思五濁之多果。慕須達
<lb ed="I" n="0257a06" type="honorific"/>之金錢。<note n="0257004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31132"/>＝深【史】</note><app n="0257004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31132"/></rdg></app><note n="0257005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">躰＝體【史】</note><app n="0257005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">躰</rdg></app><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常。同遵正覺。共造石像壹區。高七
<lb ed="I" n="0257a07" type="honorific"/>尺五寸。莊嚴種好。垂相滿庭。慈悲道俗。咸變圜中。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a08" type="honorific"/>求勝因<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">於</unclear>曩劫。獲妙果於當今。在村<note n="0257006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠁅＝處【史】</note><app n="0257006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>中置立。南
<lb ed="I" n="0257a09" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">臨</unclear>白水。北背馬蘭。東<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">俠</unclear>洛水。西<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">望</unclear>堯山。地居<note n="0257007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30470"/>＝爽【史】</note><app n="0257007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30470"/></rdg></app>塏。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a10" type="honorific"/>眾所歸仰。藉此微功。願
<lb ed="I" n="0257a11" type="honorific"/>皇帝　陛下。与日月齊暉。群公百辟。與天壤同<note n="0257008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦿔＝蔽【史】</note><app n="0257008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦿔</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a12" type="honorific"/>□□□邑。七世父母。長居妙樂。見在眷屬。迴向上
<lb ed="I" n="0257a13" type="honorific"/>道。竊惟竹素是播演之宗。金石是記善之原。非刊
<lb ed="I" n="0257a14" type="honorific"/>非瑑。何以宣言。其<note n="0257009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">辝＝辭【史】</note><app n="0257009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">辝</rdg></app>曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a15" type="honorific"/>巍巍紫山。獨秀童童。娑羅集聖。遍滿虛空。亭□□
<lb ed="I" n="0257a16" type="honorific"/>子。出入相容。不有不無。非紫非紅。攸哉大智。實唯
<lb ed="I" n="0257a17" type="honorific"/>世尊。拯彼眾生。濟此重昏。五欲自屏。三<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">惑</unclear>無根。拔
<lb ed="I" n="0257a18" type="honorific"/>苦伊何。歸依法門。生同泡沫。滅若<note n="0257010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥥗＝電【史】</note><app n="0257010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">電</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥥗</rdg></app>飛。白日恒昭。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a19" type="honorific"/>夜月長暉。業淺福倚。道勝則肥。百年俄頃。營營何
<lb ed="I" n="0257a20" type="honorific"/>希。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">分</unclear>財奉寶。散浮圖刑。漏以金玉。飾以丹青。神光
<lb ed="I" n="0257a21" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">嚴</unclear>起。曠濟群生。舟樑苦海。曆劫踰明。
<lb ed="I" n="0257a22" type="honorific"/>建德元年歲次壬辰四月癸酉朔八日庚辰建立</p>
